            ['type' => 'section', 'heading' => 'AC Repair in NJ', 'body' => "When your air conditioner blows warm air in the middle of a July heatwave, you need AC repair in NJ that responds fast and fixes it right. Guardian Air is a licensed and insured cooling company serving homeowners across Monmouth, Middlesex, and Ocean counties with same-day air conditioning repair, honest diagnostics, and upfront, flat-rate pricing — no overtime fees and no pressure.\n\nWe repair every major brand of central air, heat pump, and ductless system. Whether your AC won't turn on, short-cycles, leaks water, or simply can't keep up, our technicians pinpoint the real cause — a failed capacitor, low refrigerant, a dirty coil, a bad contactor, or a struggling compressor — and fix it on the spot whenever possible. Most repairs are completed in a single visit because we stock common parts on every truck.\n\nEvery repair begins with a clear explanation of the problem and a flat-rate quote, so you know the cost before we start. It's cooling service the way it should be: fast, fair, and backed by a local team your neighbors trust."],
