            ['type' => 'section', 'heading' => 'Cooling Systems We Service', 'body' => "Our licensed technicians install, repair, and maintain every major type of home cooling system across New Jersey.\n\nCentral Air Conditioning — The most popular whole-home option, cooling every room evenly through your existing ductwork from a single outdoor unit.\n\nHeat Pumps — Energy-efficient electric systems that both cool and heat, an ideal year-round comfort solution for New Jersey homes.\n\nDuctless Mini-Splits — A flexible, efficient choice for homes without ductwork or for cooling specific rooms, additions, and converted spaces.\n\nWindow & Wall Units — A lower-cost option for individual rooms, perfect for smaller spaces or supplementing your main system.\n\nDual-Zone Systems — Independently control the temperature in different areas of your home, improving comfort while saving energy."],
