        return [
            ['type' => 'section', 'heading' => 'Commercial HVAC Repair & Emergency', 'body' => "When your commercial HVAC system fails on a 95-degree day, every minute of downtime costs money. Guardian Air provides fast, reliable commercial HVAC repair in NJ for businesses across Monmouth, Middlesex, and Ocean counties — minimizing disruption and getting your operation back to normal quickly.\n\nOur commercial technicians repair rooftop units (RTUs), boilers, chillers, and split systems of every size and brand. We're available 24/7 for emergencies, because a no-heat morning or a sweltering sales floor can't wait. Maintenance-plan clients receive priority dispatch, and in most cases we have a technician on-site the same day.\n\nEvery call starts with a clear diagnosis and a written quote, so there are no surprises on the invoice — just honest commercial service that keeps your business running."],
